				<wikidot:authorName>TheBlueHour</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4078000</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Novote for me. The opening is really interesting and I love the look at the technical side of the Foundation, but I really did not enjoy the over the top technobabble or the Serpent's Hand connection which came out of nowhere.</p> 
				 	]]>
